	dprr:hasNoteText "BCH 54 (1930) 490f.; names supplied in SC de, Aphrodisiensibus (Viereck, Sermo Graec. p. VII, and addenda to no. 19, p. 40)\" office-xref=\"; Fast. Mag. Vic., Degrassi 283, 288; ibid. 136, 508f.; Dio, 49, Index, and 18.6, and 33.1; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; and on Cornificiums, NS 1933, 331, no. 421; on Pompeius, see D.-G. 4.324, no. 18; on Cornificius, PIR² 2.373, no. 1503; Do Laet no. 151." .
